WEBVTT

00:02.135 --> 00:05.171
In New York City's war on crime,

00:05.171 --> 00:08.080
the worst criminal offenders
are pursued by the detectives

00:08.080 --> 00:09.609
of the Major Case Squad.

00:09.609 --> 00:12.407
These are their stories.

00:13.712 --> 00:19.645
Thank you for the dance,
Mr. Fineman.

00:19.645 --> 00:22.645
Oh, you are bruised.

00:23.160 --> 00:27.490
- Did I do that?
- No, no, it wasn't you.

00:27.490 --> 00:29.813
- Are you okay?
- I'm fine.

00:29.813 --> 00:32.186
You aren't the one who decides.

00:32.186 --> 00:33.887
I don't know how it happened.

00:33.887 --> 00:34.899
Let's not make a fuss.

00:34.899 --> 00:36.812
Is everything all right at home, Lena?

00:36.812 --> 00:39.997
Everything's fine.
Please, I'm okay.

00:39.997 --> 00:42.997
Thank you for the meds, Doctor.

00:43.791 --> 00:45.963
The down payment was present enough.

00:45.963 --> 00:48.963
But if you want to,
you can make empanadas for my party.

00:49.988 --> 00:52.445
Honey, we can't go.

00:52.445 --> 00:54.445
Your dad's got a huge deadline.

00:54.445 --> 00:55.557
He always does.

00:55.557 --> 00:58.821
But you can come,
can't you?

00:58.821 --> 01:02.900
It's better I stay home.
I'm so proud of you.

01:02.900 --> 01:04.674
Claire, you got a good job.

01:04.674 --> 01:07.440
And now your own home.
This is what a mother works for.

01:07.440 --> 01:10.440
Love you too, Mom.

01:10.531 --> 01:14.172
Oh, that's nasty.
How'd you get that?

01:14.172 --> 01:16.491
From work. Don't worry.

01:16.491 --> 01:20.098
Let's find you something nice.

01:22.167 --> 01:25.631
Honey, I'm home.

01:30.186 --> 01:32.784
Honey?

01:35.668 --> 01:38.668
How long are we gonna be married
before you know how I like my burgers?

01:39.369 --> 01:42.625
Stay out of my way.!

01:48.875 --> 01:52.521
Yankees lose again, Lance?

02:00.117 --> 02:02.905
- Lance, what's...
- Help me! I need a crowbar.

02:02.905 --> 02:05.667
- What's going on?
- Lena's locked herself in the basement bathroom.

02:05.667 --> 02:07.348
I don't have a key,
and she's not answering.

02:07.348 --> 02:10.348
There's... There's blood.
I think she's hurt.

02:10.878 --> 02:14.411
Lena.!
I saw her feet.

02:14.411 --> 02:15.718
She's leaning up against the door.

02:15.718 --> 02:17.990
- I think...
- There we go.

02:17.990 --> 02:20.282
Lena! Lena! Lena!

02:20.282 --> 02:22.188
Oh, my God, Lena!

