The name underneath it.

36:14.999 --> 36:18.578
It says "Levinson," doesn't it?

36:18.578 --> 36:21.058
This must be a mistake.
These are for the wrong people.

36:21.058 --> 36:25.761
No, Dad. Mom's parents changed
their name when they got married.

36:25.761 --> 36:28.770
They wanted to move up
in Argentinean society.

36:28.770 --> 36:32.373
They figured they'd have a better
chance with the name Calderera.

36:32.373 --> 36:34.101
Levinson's a Jewish name.

36:34.101 --> 36:36.825
Lena wasn't, so her parents
couldn't be Jewish.

36:36.825 --> 36:40.875
You know those Spanish words
that Lena used to use?

36:40.875 --> 36:44.343
You know, like, um,
"esfuegra."

36:46.333 --> 36:48.945
It's actually a Jewish dialect of Spanish.

36:48.945 --> 36:50.403
It's called Ladino.

36:50.403 --> 36:52.653
And she picked that up from her parents.

36:52.653 --> 36:56.150
Lena was not Jewish.

36:56.150 --> 36:59.750
L-I would have known if she was.
I could tell.

36:59.750 --> 37:02.107
Really?
You can tell?

37:02.107 --> 37:03.898
She would have told me.
Twenty-two years of marriage,

37:03.898 --> 37:05.807
she would have said something.

37:05.807 --> 37:08.807
She didn't know till she saw the certificates.

37:10.999 --> 37:13.108
This is not possible.

37:13.108 --> 37:17.669
Dad, if Mom was Jewish,
then so am I.

37:17.669 --> 37:21.866
- Don't say that!
- It's true.

37:21.866 --> 37:24.263
You are not Jewish.
You are my daughter.

37:24.263 --> 37:27.312
And don't you dare accuse your
poor deceased mother of being a...

37:27.312 --> 37:29.747
Accuse?

37:29.747 --> 37:32.696
My wife was not a Jewess.

37:32.696 --> 37:35.696
You are not a Jewess.

37:37.441 --> 37:40.290
Claire. Claire.

37:40.290 --> 37:42.405
Claire.
Claire, please stop!

37:42.405 --> 37:43.699
Tell her these are lies.

37:43.699 --> 37:45.670
If this were true,
Lena would have told me.

37:45.670 --> 37:48.291
Uh, you think so?
Knowing how you feel aboutJews?

37:48.291 --> 37:49.798
I don't care aboutJews.

37:49.798 --> 37:51.745
You don't care about them?

37:51.745 --> 37:54.837
Even after what that Jewish man
did to your mother?

37:54.837 --> 37:57.455
Your sister told us.

37:57.455 --> 37:58.525
Be quiet about my mother.

37:58.525 --> 38:04.889
- I don't wanna hear about...
- I do. I wanna know.

38:04.889 --> 38:10.551
His mother was raped by herJewish boss.

38:10.551 --> 38:13.091
That's the way the story goes.

38:13.091 --> 38:19.082
I mean, maybe she just,
you know, liked Jewish men.

38:19.082 --> 38:22.394
You know? They excited her.
The whole forbidden fruit.

38:22.394 --> 38:25.116
You shut your dirty mouth.
He took advantage of her.

38:25.116 --> 38:26.696
He raped her.

38:26.696 --> 38:28.868
Is that why your dad beat your mom, huh?

38:28.868 --> 38:30.836
Why he broke her shoulder with an andiron?

38:30.836 --> 38:33.130
Because he couldn't do it to theJew.

38:33.130 --> 38:35.670
That guy had connections.
My dad would have lost his job.

38:35.670 --> 38:37.900
- You could have done something?
- What? I was too young.

38:37.900 --> 38:41.364
So you did nothing.
You just watched your dad...

38:41.364 --> 38:45.965
beat your mom to a pulp.
Watched him tear your family apart.

38:45.965 --> 38:48.605
- All because of theJew?
- Yes.

38:48.605 --> 38:50.078
You couldn't protect your mom?

38:50.078 --> 38:52.516
Even when she got sick,
that was his fault too?

38:52.516 --> 38:55.280
She got cancer down there where theJew had been.

38:55.280 --> 38:57.145
- He infected her.
- Stop it!

38:57.145 --> 38:59.604
The disease,
it ate her up.

38:59.604 --> 39:01.643
And you could do nothing,

39:01.643 --> 39:06.939
except for, well, choke...
on your rage and your hate.

39:06.939 --> 39:10.356
And then her death,
well, that was too much, Lance.

39:10.356 --> 39:12.609
You couldn't keep it in anymore.

39:12.609 --> 39:15.741
You had to make him pay.

39:15.741 --> 39:18.741
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

39:19.955 --> 39:22.535
But he was long dead, huh?

39:22.535 --> 39:24.688
Long dead,
but there were plenty.

39:24.688 --> 39:27.187
Plenty of men like him, huh?

39:27.187 --> 39:31.399
Pushy, grabby, arrogantJews.

39:31.399 --> 39:33.470
Thirty years you waited, right?

39:33.470 --> 39:35.499
How'd it feel?
Did it feel good?

39:35.499 --> 39:39.300
- I didn't kill anyone.
- Mark Simmons. Rafe Benjamin.

39:39.300 --> 39:41.228
- No!
- You owed it to her, huh?

39:41.228 --> 39:43.809
Jeff Demsky. Sam Landau.

39:43.809 --> 39:46.809
Stop it!

39:51.228 --> 39:54.338
Lena figured it out.

39:54.338 --> 39:56.530
Imagine how she felt.

39:56.530 --> 39:59.813
- A Jewish woman married to a Jew killer.
- I'm not.

39:59.813 --> 40:03.140
The horror that you used her
to find your victims.

40:03.140 --> 40:04.209
Not true!

40:04.209 --> 40:08.998
The terror...that one day you might
turn your rage against your own daughter.

40:08.998 --> 40:11.435
- Never. I would never do that.!
- Your own Jewish daughter.

40:11.435 --> 40:14.435
Never!

40:16.343 --> 40:19.375
Lena wasn't gonna take that chance.

40:19.375 --> 40:24.198
She couldn't prove that you killed those men,

40:24.198 --> 40:27.125
But she knew.

40:27.125 --> 40:29.930
And if she couldn't send you
to jail for killing them,

40:29.930 --> 40:33.817
