40:33.817 --> 40:36.685
This is all a bunch of lies.
All of it.

40:36.685 --> 40:38.670
Claire, I know these people.

40:38.670 --> 40:40.842
They'll say anything.
Claire, come on.

40:40.842 --> 40:43.718
I loved your mother,
but she was sick.

40:43.718 --> 40:45.787
Why, because she was Jewish?

40:45.787 --> 40:48.530
Stop saying that!

40:48.530 --> 40:51.970
You know, there's one thing that Lena overlooked.

40:51.970 --> 40:54.637
She had the proof.

40:54.637 --> 40:56.482
She just didn't realize it.

40:56.482 --> 40:59.063
The piece of paper she found in your coveralls.

40:59.063 --> 41:01.234
The one with Landau's plate number.

41:01.234 --> 41:03.939
She made a photocopy of it
and gave it to your neighbor.

41:03.939 --> 41:05.989
Oh, what, so now you're gonna
bring Richie into this?

41:05.989 --> 41:08.549
Lena asked him to call the D.M.V.

41:08.549 --> 41:11.150
That's how she found out it was Landau's number.

41:11.150 --> 41:15.863
And the paper is gone.
I mean, you probably got rid of it.

41:15.863 --> 41:21.423
But your neighbor,
he made a photocopy of it.

41:21.423 --> 41:25.191
This is Landau's plate number
in your handwriting.

41:25.191 --> 41:26.623
This is some damn trick.
Let me see that.

41:26.623 --> 41:30.572
- No, sorry. This is...
- Let me see it!

41:30.572 --> 41:34.499
Anybody can copy handwriting.

41:34.499 --> 41:36.956
You're trying to scare me.

41:36.956 --> 41:40.456
This isn't even the right number.

41:40.456 --> 41:43.456
- It's not Landau's number?
- No. It's...

41:46.318 --> 41:49.307
Well, how do you know it's not?

41:49.307 --> 41:52.560
Oh, God! Claire.

41:52.560 --> 41:55.059
You know, because you stalked Sam Landau.

41:55.059 --> 41:58.497
You memorized his number.

41:58.497 --> 42:00.853
You tricked me.
You see this, Claire?

42:00.853 --> 42:05.005
You see this?
This is just the kind of
sneaky thing you people do.

42:05.005 --> 42:07.401
Sneaky?

42:07.401 --> 42:10.492
- Like seducing your mother?
- Tha tJew raped her.

42:10.492 --> 42:13.184
ThoseJews got everything
they had coming to them.

42:13.184 --> 42:15.378
I had a right,
after what they did to your grandmother.

42:15.378 --> 42:17.897
Your mother.!
They killed your mother.!

42:17.897 --> 42:20.497
- All right, enough.
- Get your filthy hands off of me!

42:20.497 --> 42:23.534
Lance Brody,
you're under arrest.

42:23.534 --> 42:26.276
I know what you are!

42:26.276 --> 42:28.733
Look what they do to your father, Claire!

42:28.733 --> 42:31.638
You're not one of them.!
Don't believe it.!

42:31.638 --> 42:33.749
She's not a Jew!

42:33.749 --> 42:36.576
My daughter!
Can't you tell?

42:36.576 --> 42:42.163
Just look at her!
She's not one of them!

42:43.649 --> 42:48.719
Claire.!Claire.!

42:50.915 --> 42:53.915
Lena got what she wanted.

